#1
x<-c(4,8,9,10,12,14,6,10,7,11)
y<-c(9,20,22,15,17,30,18,25,11,19)
xbar<-mean(x)
ybar<-mean(y)
r<-sum((x-xbar)*(y-ybar))/sqrt(sum((x-xbar)^2)*sum((y-ybar)^2))
print(r)
## [1] 0.7180981
#2
beta<-sum((x-xbar)*(y-ybar))/sum((x-xbar)^2) 
alpha<-ybar-beta*xbar
print(beta)
## [1] 1.513308
print(alpha)
## [1] 4.828897
#3
yhat<-alpha+beta*x
sst<-sum((y-ybar)^2)
sse<-sum((y-yhat)^2)
Rsquare<-(sst-sse)/sst
print(Rsquare)
## [1] 0.5156649
